title: Adobe CC Collection June 2017 (Selective Download) {Mac OS X}
description:
Creative Cloud offers the best creative tools in the world, always up to date. And now, all the apps and resources, including new Adobe Stock images are always at your fingertips right there where they serve. And everything is perfectly connected through Adobe CreativeSync technology, so you can easily turn your brightest ideas in your best projects across desktops and mobile devices. MAKE IT. CREATIVE CLOUD. 

What includes? 
Adobe Photoshop CC 2017 v18.1.1 
Adobe Photoshop Lightroom CC v6.10.1 
Adobe After Effects CC 2017 v14.2.1 
Adobe Premiere Pro CC 2017 v11.1.2 
Adobe Animate CC 2017 v16.5.0 
Adobe Audition CC 2017 v10.1 
Adobe Bridge CC 2017 v7.0.0 
Adobe Dreamweaver CC 2017 v17.5.0 
Adobe Illustrator CC 2017 v21.1.0 
Adobe InCopy CC 2017 v12.0.0.81 
Adobe InDesign CC 2017 v12.1.0 
Adobe Media Encoder CC 2017 v11.1.2 
Adobe Muse CC 2017 v2017.0.3 
Adobe Captivate 2017 v10.0.0 

System Requirements: 
- Multicore Intel processor with 64-bit support 
- macOS version 10.12 (Sierra), Mac OS X version 10.11 (El Capitan), or Mac OS X version 10.10 (Yosemite) 
- 2 GB of RAM (8 GB recommended) 
- 4 GB of available hard-disk space for installation; additional free space required during installation (cannot install on a volume that uses a case-sensitive file system) 
- 1024 x 768 display (1280x800 recommended) with 16-bit color and 512 MB of dedicated VRAM; 2 GB is recommended* 
- OpenGL 2.0–capable system 
- Internet connection and registration are necessary for required software activation, membership validation, and access to online services
